	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00">好！<delay20 />這個地方就是我的了！</message>
	<message label="008_01" attrib="00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧有你，<delay8 />我才能做出決定！<delay20 />
